org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.cli.store

Class StoreLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.cli.store.StoreLoader

  • public class StoreLoader
extends Object
    This is a convenience class which sets up some obvious values in the OperationParams based on the parsed 'store name' from the main parameter. The other parameters are saved in case they need to be used.
